data.description: 5 bedroom home in search of new owners in Pomerene. Granite counter tops, white cabinets, pantry and stainless steel appliances are a few kitchen perks. Second floor master suite has spacious walk in closet, dual sinks, separate shower/toilet room and extra wall cabinets for linens. Spacious bedrooms and closets on both floors and a unique layout separate this listing from comparable homes. The extra roomy laundry room includes a saltless water softener, a large tankless water heater, storage shelves, a sink and plenty of space for freezers, or a folding table. The backyard is fully fenced, includes a dog run and block kennels. Plenty of space for a large garden, pool or your own designed landscaping. Ride ATV's out the back gate and never need to trailer again! Floor plan in photos!
